---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About">

  <section class="about">

    <h1>About</h1>

    <p>
      Hello, I’m Sameer Rahman. I build AI-powered SaaS products and automation systems.
    </p>

    <p>
      I enjoy taking ideas and turning them into real, working products. Instead of overthinking or planning endlessly, I prefer to start building, test quickly, and improve over time. For me, execution matters more than anything else.
    </p>

    <p>
      Most of my work is focused on creating practical tools that solve real problems. I use modern web technologies along with AI APIs to build systems that are simple, fast, and useful. I try to avoid unnecessary complexity and focus on what actually works.
    </p>

    <p>
      I’m particularly interested in how AI can be integrated into everyday products. Not just as an extra feature, but as a core part of how the product works. A lot of what I build revolves around exploring that idea.
    </p>

    <p>
      Over time, I’ve worked on different projects, experimented with ideas, and learned through trial and error. Some things work, some don’t, but every project helps me improve and understand things better.
    </p>

    <p>
      This site is where I share what I learn along the way. Sometimes it’s about building products, sometimes about systems, and sometimes just lessons from experience. I keep things simple and write based on real work, not theory.
    </p>

    <p>
      I believe in building in public, improving continuously, and learning by doing. Everything I create evolves over time, and that process is part of what makes building interesting.
    </p>

    <p>
      My goal is to keep building useful products, grow them step by step, and create systems that actually make an impact.
    </p>

  </section>

  <style>
    .about {
      margin-top: 10px;
      max-width: 600px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #aaa;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    body.light p {
      color: #555;
    }
  </style>

</Layout>